highlights.text: “Mind Loaded (feat. Caroline Polachek, Lorde & Mustafa)” by Blood Orange, Caroline Polachek, Lorde, and Mustafa is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 21 spots at #42.
Diego Mitre has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “To the Infinity Castle - Muzan vs Hashira Theme (from "Demon Slayer") - Cover” is the highest at #3.
“おつかれSUMMER” by HALCALI has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 117 days straight.
“TOMA NO BAILÃO” by DJ FKU is the highest new entry on Viral Songs South Korea at #64.
